				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Can any expert Magicians here clarify what exactly the burnout line of spells do?  They seem to increase the pets combat and such, but I am not exactly sure in what ways.  I have read different things on it such as it damages your pets over time like a dot or that it prevents or slows regeneration.  Any of this true?  I have always been using it since I first got the spell as if were just a good pet buff, but I am wondering if there is anything about the spell I should be aware of.  Are there times when I shouldn't use it?  etc.
